data.description: Assumable interest rate available of 2.75%, buyer must qualify through lender. Contact agent for more info! Beautiful home in Quincy Park located in Frenship ISD.  Built in 2018, this home features a large living/kitchen area as the central area of the home.  The kitchen features a large table & eating area, large island with bar area, built in stainless steel appliances, large pantry and beautiful granite countertops.  There is also an adjacent room that could be used for a formal dining room, 2nd living area or it could make a great home office.  There is plenty of room for everyone, as two of the four bedrooms are isolated. This home is in great condition! Grab your favorite realtor and schedule an appointment to see this house today.
